des, specialty plant nutrition products, and crop care chemicals through a network of distributors; hybrid seeds for field and vegetable crops, corn, and paddy; and operates fuel outlets. The company was incorporated in 1989 and is based in New Delhi, India. DCM Shriram Limited operates as a subsidiary of Sumant Investments Pvt Ltd."}}